# __PLUGIN_TITLE__

Generated plugin scaffold for Ghost shell runtime.

- Keep imports on `@ghost/plugin-contracts` public exports.
- Start with `src/index.ts` and evolve contributions as needed.
- For core shell flows, model invocations with `contributes.actions` and object `when` predicates (including menu/keybinding gating).
- Default shell keyboard behavior is browser-safe and modifier-based (`Shift+Alt` / `Ctrl+Alt` families) without requiring `Meta/Super` bindings.
